---
name: nlp-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for Natural Language Processing (NLP) in data pipelines
globs: **/*.py
---

- Preprocess text data (tokenization, normalization) to improve model performance.
- Use pre-trained models for common tasks to save time and resources.
- Implement batch processing for NLP tasks to handle large volumes of data efficiently.
- Regularly evaluate model performance and retrain with new data as necessary.
- Ensure that the NLP pipeline is modular for easy updates and maintenance.
